title: File:18th East Asia Summit, Jakarta, Indonesia (2).jpg
author: BPMI Sekretariat Presiden/Muchlis Jr.
description: President Joko Widodo officially opened the 18th East Asia Summit which was held at Cendrawasih 3 Room of the Jakarta Convention Center, Jakarta, on Thursday, 7 September 2023. In his opening remarks, the president affirmed that ASEAN has strengthen its determination to make the region as an epicenter of growth.
